      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://jianchao-li.github.io/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Jianchao Li is a software engineer based in Zurich, Switzerland, currently working at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.meta.com/&#34;&gt;Meta&lt;/a&gt;. His work focuses on deep learning, machine learning, and computer vision. Before Meta, he worked at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.visenze.com/&#34;&gt;ViSenze&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.bytedance.com/&#34;&gt;ByteDance&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.indeed.com/&#34;&gt;Indeed&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;experience&#34;&gt;Experience&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;timeline&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;timeline-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;timeline-marker&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.meta.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;nozoom&#34; src=&#34;meta.png&#34; alt=&#34;Meta&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;timeline-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;Software Engineer at Meta&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;timeline-date&#34;&gt;January 2021 - Present&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;timeline-location&#34;&gt;Zurich, Switzerland&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;timeline-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;timeline-marker&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.visenze.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;nozoom&#34; src=&#34;visenze.png&#34; alt=&#34;ViSenze&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;timeline-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;Research Engineer at ViSenze&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;timeline-date&#34;&gt;June 2019 - December 2020&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;timeline-location&#34;&gt;Singapore&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;timeline-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;timeline-marker&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.bytedance.com/&#34; target=&#3